{"id":"dba76956-75fc-4acc-8c4a-493d5b587bcc","title":"1553/04/22: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"0d5c3230-ae4f-4793-86bd-bf8eef14ee04","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, April 22nd, 1553.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"1f9444b3-4647-4ad6-baf1-94189ef891d1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"cefe6ee2-fd35-4de1-b306-a03a14431c14","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":26,"value":"bdecca79-11f3-4f66-b408-55a479845a53","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5f18d51f-4cd3-4961-9e34-c74e8a37b651","type":"style/superscript","start":19,"end":20,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"e3491883-8f66-471d-a41c-21ab8b30198f","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d686a67c-1aa7-4bf7-a150-c457e30c5579","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8466b878-9f88-4c91-a26e-19476840da18","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"daaac128-57cf-4bc5-a125-b8238b72817a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"9bd579ea-3b44-41da-98d4-e8dc9d8758f4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"829cc76c-c015-4534-91d2-6f16979bc66d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I learn from thy last letter that the renewed negotiations in connection with Donato\u00A0Ridolfi\u0027s daughter have ended satisfactorily, thanks\u00A0be to God. I pray that by His grace the marriage may be concluded. With regard to the security for the dowry, I have had the power of attorney drawn up in thy name and am sending it with this letter so\u00A0that thou canst secure the dowry, 1,500 ducats at seven lire the ducat as mentioned by thee, by making it a charge upon whatever portion of my property seemeth to thee most suitable. I have spoken with\u00A0Messer Lorenzo Ridolfi, and I greeted him in the proper form as well as I was able. I have no more to add at the moment. Thou wilt let me know how the affair proceeds, and I will try and think of some\u00A0present to send her according to custom.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c2cacec2-efb1-4b8c-add8-0fefb8fd8372","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"89fb3649-3950-4fb7-bf95-a60733a71305","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2b19efa1-bc1c-4441-853a-f4f1a43e7239","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f497ba0a-80c4-46d2-91ac-104916bcad76","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":25,"end":27,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"05ac5df3-83a8-4063-8310-063b3abac4db","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":90,"end":103,"value":"aa840561-5d98-4227-bc3a-551254787379","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d10f444c-ad89-4b36-a805-b32c7ff31dea","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":107,"end":114,"value":"406b9dc0-8e0d-46e3-bfd8-aeb93346e8be","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"06f1d680-ea74-4e44-b9db-75cbb22a6d7b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":156,"end":158,"value":"a3fed3ec-1814-4027-a2d5-ac598b2fcb6f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d0c0e4c8-0c1b-43cf-a90e-ebd7cb6c863d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":161,"end":161,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c12b8638-7fbc-4ad5-9fae-a2eb7c2fd9c9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":176,"end":178